net.dean.jraw.models

Class MoreChildren

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.models.JsonModel
      • net.dean.jraw.models.RedditObject
        • net.dean.jraw.models.Thing
          • net.dean.jraw.models.MoreChildren

  • @Model(kind=MORE)
public class MoreChildren
extends Thing
    This class represents a list of Thing IDs. This element, when present, is the last element of a Listing in the JSON response. The purpose of this data structure is to notify the client that there are more replies to a comment than what Reddit is willing to initially show.
    See Also:
    CommentNode.getMoreChildren(), CommentNode.loadMoreComments(RedditClient)
